verbose_text: Cyclin C binding to Drp1 in the presence of non hydrolyzable GTP analog beta, gamma-methyleneguanosine 5 '-triphosphate (GMP-PCP) induces formation of longer filaments by disassembling non productive Drp1 rings and small filaments.
